room_title: Escape room "Cuckoo's Nest" by Key To Escape in Nashua
room_description: It's 1948, and you've arrived at Nashua's Hospital for the Criminally Insane. You thought you were coming to consult with one of the psychiatrists, but things take a turn when you get locked in a padded cell instead of being taken to an interview room! You have one hour before the facility goes into lockdown, leaving you with no hope for escape. Are you sane enough to escape before it's too late?
